# Registry SCOPING only — never commit credentials here.
# Auth (username + _password) belongs in your user npmrc (%USERPROFILE%\.npmrc)
# or the root .env (NPM_REGISTRY_USERNAME / NPM_REGISTRY_PASSWORD) consumed by
# `pnpm install:deps`. See .env.npmrc.example.
@igrp:registry=https://sonatype.nosi.cv/repository/igrp/
//sonatype.nosi.cv/repository/igrp/:always-auth=true
